==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Greencloth
<hw>Green"cloth`</hw> <pr>(-kl⟦ocr⟧th`; 115)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A
board or court of justice formerly held in the counting house of the
British sovereign's household, composed of the lord steward and his
officers, and having cognizance of matters of justice in the household,
with power to correct offenders and keep the peace within the verge of
the palace, which extends two hundred yards beyond the gates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Greenery</ent>⟦br⟧
